00:10:50.270 --> 00:10:53.390
So we pretended we were live.

00:10:53.390 --> 00:10:55.760
So we had weekly
content releases,

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:57.980
we had our weekly
reviews on marketing

00:10:57.980 --> 00:11:00.740
spend, we did social
media, customer care.

00:11:00.740 --> 00:11:02.810
We did everything as if
we were live globally,

00:11:02.810 --> 00:11:06.320
just limited to the UK,
across all platforms.

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:09.639
And we didn't do that to
evaluate if the game would work

00:11:09.639 --> 00:11:11.930
from a retention perspective--
we had already done that

00:11:11.930 --> 00:11:12.870
before--

00:11:12.870 --> 00:11:15.650
but to practice if we
could run life operations,

00:11:15.650 --> 00:11:17.480
if we could run
content production,

00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:20.940
if we could run localization
and all of those things.

00:11:20.940 --> 00:11:22.980
