To have those dozens of
people who are involved,

00:12:03.020 --> 00:12:05.930
to basically prepare them,
and train them and get them

00:12:05.930 --> 00:12:09.680
into the rhythm of what it
means to run a game with life

00:12:09.680 --> 00:12:11.810
