00:22:47.476 --> 00:22:48.850
SAAD CHOUDRI: Soft
global launch.

00:22:48.850 --> 00:22:50.600
JENS BEGEMANN: Soft
global launch is not--

00:22:50.600 --> 00:22:52.058
SAAD CHOUDRI:
Somebody in this room

00:22:52.058 --> 00:22:53.540
will come up with a better idea.

00:22:53.540 --> 00:22:55.450
JENS BEGEMANN: Sorry
we interrupted you.

00:22:55.450 --> 00:22:57.390
AUDIENCE: I was just
curious of what learnings

00:22:57.390 --> 00:22:58.940
did you get from that?

00:22:58.940 --> 00:23:02.660
You did the rehearsal and
