00:23:02.660 --> 00:23:04.340
Saad, you did all
your campaigns,

00:23:04.340 --> 00:23:06.680
and did you learn
anything from it?

00:23:06.680 --> 00:23:10.519
Did that affect the way you ran
the global launch after that?

00:23:10.519 --> 00:23:11.810
SAAD CHOUDRI: Yeah, absolutely.

00:23:11.810 --> 00:23:14.000
That's why you do it right.

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:17.180
Some of the channels in which
we had spent some marketing

00:23:17.180 --> 00:23:23.510
dollars, we scaled that back,
other ones we put more into it.

00:23:23.510 --> 00:23:28.700
For us, it was a new type of
genre for us to enter into.

00:23:28.700 --> 00:23:31.190
We just really wanted
to make sure that one,

00:23:31.190 --> 00:23:35.210
did our own network respond
to that kind of game?

00:23:35.210 --> 00:23:37.200
What kind of UA channels?

00:23:37.200 --> 00:23:39.560
Does brand marketing
campaigns work for this?

00:23:39.560 --> 00:23:41.540
That's what we got from that.

00:23:41.540 --> 00:23:44.180
We took that data back
and then rearranged

00:23:44.180 --> 00:23:47.120
what we did for global launch.

00:23:47.120 --> 00:23:51.154
We wouldn't have got that had we
