I invite you all to come and
find our panelists afterwards

00:28:50.105 --> 00:28:52.130
at the break if you
want to pick their brain

00:28:52.130 --> 00:28:55.310
and get some more
specific advice.

00:28:55.310 --> 00:28:59.450
I wish you a very successful
